dct_description_sm: United States. Central Intelligence Agency. Cartography Center. Relief shown by shading. Lambert conformal conic projection. Inset maps: Bagdad (1:316,800); area comparison map, and radial distance map. "803079A1 (C00503) 7-04." Also available via Internet from the Library of Congress Website as a raster image.
